	8. ``South Park: Bigger, Longer and Uncut,'' $7.1 million.  
</P>
<P>
	9. ``Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me,'' $6.5 million.  
</P>
<P>
	10. ``Summer of Sam,'' $3.4 million.  
  	   	
