<HEADLINE> Red Sox Activate John Valentin </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ATLANTA (AP) -- The Boston Red Sox activated third baseman John  
Valentin from the 15-day disabled list Sunday and optioned 
infielder Chad Fonville to Triple-A Pawtucket. 
</P>
